212
00:10:23,330 --> 00:10:24,489
Scott: They just have to turn ActiveSync on.

213
00:10:24,650 --> 00:10:24,746
Scott: Done.

214
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:25,270
Scott: One click.

215
00:10:25,490 --> 00:10:30,870
