216
00:10:31,133 --> 00:10:32,770
Rym: A lot of them don't have their own smartphone.

217
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:35,029
Rym: A lot of them are happy to have gotten the work smartphone.

218
00:10:37,010 --> 00:10:41,570
