00:19:08,670 --> 00:19:09,900
Scott: Straight up legal, right?

359
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:11,110
Scott: I mean, they're blackmailing something.

360
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:11,901
Rym: Well, independently.

