00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:06,354
Scott: Yeah, I don't really care enough.

434
00:22:06,575 --> 00:22:13,230
Scott: I guess if it was, you know, I mean, if it was like a Mozilla situation where I know they have bounties, I would just be like, hey, you have a bounty I'd like to collect.

