904
00:44:54,471 --> 00:45:01,570
Scott: And what will happen is it'll take pages if your RAM is full and it still needs to put more things in the RAM because it can't work directly off the disk.

905
00:45:01,650 --> 00:45:02,979
Scott: It has to work off, you know, has to.

906
00:45:03,240 --> 00:45:05,211
